Title: Pocahontas 2: Journey to a New World
Genre: Animation, Adventure, Drama, Family, Musical, Romance
Writer: Allen Estrin (screenplay), Cindy Marcus (screenplay), Flip Kobler (screenplay)
Actors: Irene Bedard, Jim Cummings, Donal Gibson, Finola Hughes
Plot: Pocahontas sets off on a journey to England with Meeko, Flit, and Percy. Hearing rumors of John Smith's death, Pocahontas tries to prevent war and battle.
